block main
    section
        h2 Copyediting
            p.hatnote #[a(href='/copyediting') Return to more recent work.]
            h3 Press releases and event write-ups
                p From April to June 2023, I interned with #[a(href='https://ivparks.org') Isla Vista Recreation & Park District], writing press releases and event recaps by #[strong interviewing event attendees in a journalistic style]. I also helped refine the wording of social media posts, newsletters, and the website, in the process creating a style guide of commonly used words and grammatical structures by referencing #[i The Chicago Manual of Style] and #[i Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary].
                ul
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-APIDA-Heritage-Month-Celebration-press-release.pdf') Press release: APIDA Heritage Month Celebration]
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Concert-for-the-Coast-press-release.pdf') Press release: Concert for the Coast]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Cinco-de-Mayo-Celebration-Press-Release.pdf') Press release: Cinco de Mayo Celebration]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Generation-Recovery-Press-Release.pdf') Press release: Generation Recovery]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-EAB-IV-Earth-Day-press-release.pdf') Press release: EAB IV Earth Day]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Art-in-the-Park-press-release.pdf') Press release: Art in the Park]
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Stewardship-Saturday-at-Sueno-Orchard-write-up.pdf') Event write-up: Stewardship Saturday at Sueño Orchard]
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-APIDA-Heritage-Month-Celebration-write-up.pdf') Event write-up: APIDA Heritage Month Celebration]
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Concert-for-the-Coast-write-up.pdf') Event write-up: Concert for the Coast]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Cinco-de-Mayo-Celebration-write-up.pdf') Event write-up: Cinco de Mayo Celebration]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-Generation-Recovery-write-up.pdf') Event write-up: Generation Recovery]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-EAB-IV-Earth-Day-write-up.pdf') Event write-up: EAB IV Earth Day]
                    li.starred Website editing: Parks (#[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-website-parks-before.pdf') before] and #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-website-parks-after.pdf') after])
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/IVRPD-style-guide.pdf') Style guide]
            h3 Research papers
                p From February to June 2023, I helped copyedit a research paper about #[strong Joan Didion's writing and mental health]. We corresponded via email and swapped drafts. To maintain consistency, I created a style guide that referenced #[i The Chicago Manual of Style] and #[i Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary].
                ul
                    li.starred #[i Behind the Shades: A Close Look at the Blurred Lines between Joan Didion's Fiction and Nonfiction] (#[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Didion-before.pdf') before] and #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Didion-after.pdf') after])
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Didion-style-guide.pdf') Style guide]
            h3 Miscellaneous
                p These show that I know the standard copyediting marks and can edit by hand, for stories that are printed on paper.
                ul
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Class-public-radio-editing.pdf') Radio]
                    li.starred #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Class-Today-Im-Yours-editing.pdf') "Today I'm Yours"]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Class-syphilis-editing.pdf') Syphilis]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Class-tattooing-editing.pdf') Tattooing]
    section
        h2 Web
            p.hatnote #[a(href='/web') Return to more recent work.]
            h3 #[i The Catalyst Literary Arts Magazine]
                p From September 2022 to November 2023, I #[strong redesigned, updated, and maintained #[i The Catalyst]'s' WordPress website]. I directly edited the site’s HTML and CSS to customize its appearance and improve its usability on mobile devices.
                ul
                    li Before (#[a(href='https://web.archive.org/web/20210624100817/http://catalyst.english.ucsb.edu/') Wayback Machine] and #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Catalyst-website-before.png') image])
                    li After (#[a(href='https://web.archive.org/web/20231127042937/https://catalyst.english.ucsb.edu/') Wayback Machine] and #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Catalyst-website-after.png') image])
                p I also created a series of 9 videos that instructed future students on how to update and maintain the website themselves. Below is a selection.
                ul
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/catalyst-v01-final-introduction-and-logging-in/') V01 Introduction and logging in]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/catalyst-v03-final-editing-regular-pages/') V03 Editing regular pages]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/catalyst-v05-final-dashboard/') V05 Dashboard]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/catalyst-v06-final-creating-launch-pages/') V06 Creating launch pages]
                    li #[a(href='https://platypiduses.com/9-final-destroying-engineers-with-chatgpt/') V09 Destroying engineers with ChatGPT]